CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1778825170
OL,3,CWill Eurovision stay 'United By Music'
OL,4,Cas countries boycott over Israel?
OL,6,FSitting in on the dress rehearsals
OL,7,Fduring the Eurovision song contest
OL,8,Fweek, you can't help but be struck by
OL,9,Fhow spectacular the staging of the
OL,10,Fevent is.
OL,12,FIt always is. But staging aside, this
OL,13,Fis not exactly how organisers would've
OL,14,Fwanted this - the 70th anniversary of
OL,15,Fthe world's biggest live cultural
OL,16,Fevent - to have gone.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1778825170
OL,3,CWill Eurovision stay 'United By Music'
OL,4,Cas countries boycott over Israel?
OL,6,FThere have been boycotts before, but
OL,7,Fthis year, five countries have dropped
OL,8,Fout, including one, Spain, which is
OL,9,Fpart of the so-called big five - the
OL,10,Fgroup of countries which financially
OL,11,Fcontribute the most to the European
OL,12,FBroadcasting Union (EBU) and therefore
OL,13,Fget automatic qualification for the
OL,14,FEurovision final.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1778825170
OL,3,CWill Eurovision stay 'United By Music'
OL,4,Cas countries boycott over Israel?
OL,6,FThe others making a stand this year
OL,7,Fbecause of the competition's inclusion
OL,8,Fof Israel are the Netherlands,
OL,9,FIceland, Ireland, which are joint
OL,10,Frecord holders here with seven wins in
OL,11,Fthe past, and Slovenia, which
OL,12,Fneighbours this year's host country,
OL,13,FAustria.
OL,15,FSome of those countries' broadcasters
OL,16,Fwill not even be showing the
OL,17,Fcompetition, breaking with decades of
OL,18,Fpractice.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1778825170
OL,3,CWill Eurovision stay 'United By Music'
OL,4,Cas countries boycott over Israel?
OL,6,FBut Eurovision's director Martin Green
OL,7,Fsaid fans can still access the show on
OL,8,FYouTube.
OL,10,FWhere we see five countries dropping
OL,11,Fout this year, he's focusing on the 35
OL,12,Fcountries that are in, including
OL,13,FHungary's return, where a change in
OL,14,Fgovernment has prompted a renewed wish
OL,15,Fto be part of the Eurovision family.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1778825170
OL,3,CWill Eurovision stay 'United By Music'
OL,4,Cas countries boycott over Israel?
OL,6,FBut this has been a stormy time for
OL,7,Fthe competition. Following concerns
OL,8,Fthat Israel's entry last year,
OL,9,Fperformed by Yuval Raphael, benefited
OL,10,Ffrom an Israeli government-backed
OL,11,Fcampaign urging the Israeli diaspora
OL,12,Fto use all their available 20 votes on
OL,13,Fher, the organisation has had to adapt
OL,14,Fits rules and change the voting system.
OL,16,FBut they've already had to pull up
OL,17,FIsrael's entry this year, Noam Bettan,
OL,18,Fover his social media campaign to get
OL,19,Fvotes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1778825170
OL,3,CWill Eurovision stay 'United By Music'
OL,4,Cas countries boycott over Israel?
OL,6,FIt was not within the spirit of the
OL,7,Fcompetition, Martin Green told me.
OL,9,FWhat about accusations of hypocrisy
OL,10,Fover Russia being barred from the
OL,11,Fcompetition following its invasion of
OL,12,FUkraine, and yet Israel, following its
OL,13,Fwar in Gaza, is still being allowed to
OL,14,Fcompete?
OL,16,FThis is a competition between
OL,17,Fbroadcasters, he said and not
OL,18,Fcountries, an argument he's had to
OL,19,Fmake time and again, to the wider
OL,20,Fworld, not convinced by the
OL,21,Fdistinction.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1778825170
OL,3,CWill Eurovision stay 'United By Music'
OL,4,Cas countries boycott over Israel?
OL,6,FBut as we've seen in the last two
OL,7,Fyears, those opposing the inclusion of
OL,8,FIsrael will make their voices heard.
OL,10,FThere are protests planned over the
OL,11,Fweekend, and the Austrian broadcaster
OL,12,Fhas decided to reverse the rule on
OL,13,Fblocking out the sound of boos in the
OL,14,Fauditorium.
OL,16,FBoos could be heard as Noam Bettan
OL,17,Ftook to the stage for his semi-final
OL,18,Fon Tuesday, and four protesters were
OL,19,Fforcibly removed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
