PN,31908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1778825170
OL,3,CWill Eurovision stay 'United By Music'
OL,4,Cas countries boycott over Israel?
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FThe show's organisers are on alert, as
OL,12,Fare the police and security forces in
OL,13,FAustria's capital, Vienna.
OL,15,FWe have become increasingly used to
OL,16,Fthese Eurovision preparations, since
OL,17,Fthe war in Gaza has mobilised pro-
OL,18,FPalestinian supporters, who have
OL,19,Ffocused their opposition on Eurovision
OL,20,Fsince 2024.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1778825170
OL,3,CWill Eurovision stay 'United By Music'
OL,4,Cas countries boycott over Israel?
OL,6,FBut someone will win the competition
OL,7,Fon Saturday night, and then for
OL,8,Forganisers, headaches may start all
OL,9,Fover again.
OL,11,FIsrael is among the favourites, and if
OL,12,Fthey win, that would open up a whole
OL,13,Fnew challenge for the EBU, and for the
OL,14,Fcountries who continue to support a
OL,15,Fcompetition whose motto is 'United By
OL,16,FMusic'.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
